<div class="white section">

  <div class="section-title" style="padding-bottom: 10px;">
    Core Team Requirements
  </div>

  <p>You must be enrolled as a student at Cornell University.</p>
  <p>Applying developers should have experience with iOS development, Android development, web development, or DevOps. If you have experience with more than one of those listed, that's bonus points.</p>

  <p>Applying designers should have experience in a design software like Adobe Illustrator, Sketch or the like. You will be asked for a portfolio of previous design experiences / endeavors.</p>

</div>
